# Common AWS FinOps Anti-Patterns

Avoid:

* single shared AWS account
* missing tags
* perpetual overprovisioning
* ignoring data transfer costs
* manual approvals for everything
* buying excessive Reserved Instances
* no ownership model
* optimizing only infra, not architecture

